orageString() to include deadline data.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":38,"deletions":2}}},{"hash":"971222e83ed2c5d88b8e584a70c4311584ef35c1","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add deadline date parsing support","messageBody":"Enable parsing and validation of deadline dates from user input.\n\nLet\u0027s,\n* update Parser to extract deadline arguments and validate the\n  due date format.\n* update Deadline to change the type of dueDate to be LocalDate.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":34,"deletions":3}}},{"hash":"abde88763d359016b019dc562723acb4d7b5f899","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Add LocalDate parsing for deadline input","messageBody":"Enable parsing and validation of deadline dates from user input.\n\nLet\u0027s,\n* convert deadline input strings into LocalDate objects in Parser.\n* update Deadline to store due dates as LocalDate.\n* validate date format and throw InternTrackrException for invalid input.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"functional-code":{"insertions":29,"deletions":20}}}]},{"date":"2026-03-16T00:00:00","commitResults":[{"hash":"a620357913ea2a8c260e2d84797e8cb24326e712","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"test: add unit tests for Deadline","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"test-code":{"insertions":80,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"2285b691e44cdc53c26cf1d3ccb4fc57639341e3","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"test: add unit tests for DeadlineCommand","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"test-code":{"insertions":129,"deletions":0}}},{"hash":"2364e2f181602dc530a01abff7960085d8891524","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"style: remove unnecessary throws Exception from tests","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"test-code":{"insertions":3,"deletions":3}}},{"hash":"a38ef49a224a7c311af4b61186eda317281dd3da","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"style: add trailing newline to test files","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"